fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
We must show that the forgetful functor U creates U-split
  coequalizers. Let G\xrightarrow {f, g} H be a pair of
  homomorphisms that admit a split coequalizer 




    \usepackage{tikz, tikz-cd, mathtools, amssymb}
