      Fc\ar [r, "((Gk)f^\flat )^\sharp "'] & Gd'
    \end {tikzcd}


commutes. This asserts that kf^\sharp  = ((Gk)f^\flat )^\sharp , so taking
  the transpose of both side, we find that
  (kf^\sharp )^\flat  = (Gk)f^\flat , as desired for naturality.

